name: Room
description:
Modeling of rooms:
Use in and out features to model air flows to other rooms.

Temperature = Mean Air Temperature

Modeling of wort case points in room:
Lowest Temperature = Temperature at worst case point in room. 
Lowest Temperature Minimum -> Temperature should not fall below this value.

Thermal Power Optimizer = If positive heat is drawn from the thermal inertia, if negative heat is stored.

name: Thermal Register With Internal Recirculation
description: If SetSignalValve is 0%, then 100% of MassFlowInternal remains recirculating through the heat exchanger.If set SetSignalValve is 50%, then 50% of MassFlow and 50% of MassFlowInternal is pumped through the heat exchanger . If the SetSignalValve is 100%, then no fluid is recirculating an 100% of MassFlow is pumped through the heat exchanger.

name: Three Way Valve
description: Type representing three way valves.Continuous Valve: If the Set Signal is 0%, then all of the volume flow is taken from the cold port. If the Set Signal is 100% then all of the volume flow is taken from the hot port. Binary Valve: If the unit can only switch one way or the other: ON/OFF = false means volume flow is taken from the cold port. ON/OFF = true means volume flow is taken from the hot port.
